  <relatedmaterial id="aspace_2ecbc54673e380f330014c050cbccb07">
    <head>Related Material at the Department of Prints, Photographs, and Architectural Collections</head>
<p>This collection was removed from the Architect and Engineer File (PR-003) in 2002. Photographs of work done solely by John Mead Howells is included in that File (PR-003-215). Hood's architectural drawings are held by Columbia University's Avery Library.</p>  </relatedmaterial>
